Dialogue: 0,00:13:46.91,00:13:50.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,やはりか…　スサノオ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm certain it's not a clone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected... Susano'o.
