Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The power in its attack is as expected.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:16.79,00:14:20.66,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《また…\N今のも影分身じゃなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again? So if that wasn't\Na clone either...{\i0}
