Dialogue: 0,00:15:32.04,00:15:35.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ダンゾウの能力を確かめるにしては\Nやりすぎだ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too much just to\Ntest Danzo's power.
